plot: Nia's roommate is attacked by a man targeting Dreamer; Dreamer refuses to give into men's threats and puts herself in the line of fire to stop him; Alex, J'onn and Kelly attempt to rescue a man stuck inside a virtual reality game.

While Alex and J'onn look of a man who disappeared into Obsidian's VR, in the real world Nia deal with a hate group member who is targeting the trans community - and targets Nia's roommate Yvette. Meanwhile, Kelly realizes that Obsidian isn't fixing the glitches that she's reported to them.—Gislef
